---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Uses - Sam Julien">
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Uses</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Last updated: March 2025</p>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <p>
      This is my <a href="https://uses.tech" target="_blank" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">uses page</a>, a list of hardware, software, and tools I use on a daily basis. I'm always refining my setup to optimize for productivity and comfort.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Hardware</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>MacBook Pro (M2, 16GB RAM)</li>
      <li>Dell 27" 4K monitors (dual setup)</li>
      <li>Logitech MX Master 3 mouse</li>
      <li>Keychron K2 mechanical keyboard</li>
      <li>Blue Yeti microphone</li>
      <li>Sony WH-1000XM4 noise-canceling headphones</li>
      <li>Standing desk from Fully</li>
      <li>Herman Miller Aeron chair</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Development Software</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>VS Code as my primary editor</li>
      <li>iTerm2 with Oh My Zsh</li>
      <li>GitHub Copilot for AI assistance</li>
      <li>Docker for containerization</li>
      <li>Postman for API testing</li>
      <li>Git for version control</li>
      <li>Node.js and Python for development</li>
      <li>Astro for building websites (like this one!)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Productivity Tools</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Notion for notes and project management</li>
      <li>Obsidian for personal knowledge management</li>
      <li>Alfred for quick app launching and workflows</li>
      <li>1Password for password management</li>
      <li>Calendly for scheduling</li>
      <li>Raycast for window management</li>
      <li>Grammarly for writing assistance</li>
      <li>Loom for quick screen recordings</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Content Creation</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>OBS for streaming and recording</li>
      <li>Final Cut Pro for video editing</li>
      <li>Canva for quick graphics</li>
      <li>Figma for more detailed design work</li>
      <li>Descript for podcast editing</li>
      <li>Riverside for remote interviews</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
      <p class="italic">
        Have questions about my setup? Feel free to reach out on <a href="https://x.com/samjulien" target="_blank" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">X</a> or <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/samjulien/" target="_blank" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
